
=== Environment Command ====================================

grp_col_width: <size>                   # set group column width

=== Instance Choose (Violation Report) =====================

i:<sect>:<group>:<rid>:<path>           # choose the specific instances
                                          <rid> = 0-left, 1-right, 2-all

ir:<sect>:<group>:<rid>:<regex>         # use regular expression to choose instances
                                          <rid> = 0-left, 1-right, 2-all

=== Instance Operation =====================================

<inst_path> s:<value>                   # add slack offset to the specific instances
<inst_path> r                           # reserve the instance
<inst_path> d                           # remove the instance

<inst_path> r:<condition>               # condition reserve/remove:
<inst_path> d:<condition>                   - condition format : <target><operation><value>
                                            - target           : slk (slack)
                                            - operation        : >, <, ==, >=, <=
                                            - value type       : int or float

## The priority of the command: s > r > d

=== Group Choose (Summary Report) ==========================

g:<sect>:<group>:<rid>                  # choose the specific group
                                          <rid> = 0-left, 1-right, 2-diff

gr:<sect>:<regex>:<rid>                 # use regular expression to choose group
                                          <rid> = 0-left, 1-right, 2-diff

=== Group Operation (Summary) ==============================

<group> w:<codition>                    # threshould alarm:
                                            - condition format : <target><operation><value>
                                            - target           : wns, tns, nvp
                                            - operation        : >, <, ==, >=, <=
                                            - value type       : int or float

